                            <formatted-text>
                              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold'>Operational Insight: </run>
                              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold'>This Treemap identifies high-risk inventory &apos;bottlenecks.&apos; Larger boxes represent significant shelf real estate (Facings), while </run>
                              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold'>Red</run>
                              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold'> coloring flags products at </run>
                              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold'>CRITICAL</run>
                              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold'> risk: items with high stock levels currently sitting at full price with no active discount. Immediate markdowns are recommended for highlighted Private Label gallons to mitigate waste and optimize shelf turnover</run>
                            </formatted-text>
