                            <formatted-text>
                              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold'>Insight: </run>
                              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold'>Ensures corporate alignment with community wellness goals. This leaderboard highlights products with a </run>
                              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold'>Wellness Score &gt; 60</run>
                              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold'> that are </run>
                              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold'>SNAP-eligible</run>
                              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Semibold'>. The lighter blue-coded results confirm that high-health staples (1% and Skim milks) remain priced at the lowest tiers ($1.59 - $2.19), fulfilling the strategic mission of keeping nutrition affordable.</run>
                            </formatted-text>
                            <zone-style>
